=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
תּחת / tachath / takh'-ath
=== Etymology ===

From the same as H8430; 

=== Preposition ===

the bottom (as depressed); only adverbially [[below]] (often with prepositional prefix underneath), in lieu of, etc.: - as, [[beneath]], X flat, in (-stead), (same) place (where . . . is), room, for . . . sake, stead of, under, X unto, X when . . . was mine, whereas, [where-] fore, with.